text: Ryan Andrew Prescott (born 21 January 1989) is an English actor. He is best known his the role as Ryan Connor on the long-running ITV soap opera Coronation Street, he began starring in the role in 2018. In 2011, Prescott played the role of Flynn Buchanan in ITV's fellow soap opera Emmerdale. Prescott was born in Southport, England. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Entertainers from Merseyside Category:People from Southport
